{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"签名（安全）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Signature/Security","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>签名</strong>或<em>数字签名</em>是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">协议</a>，表明消息是真实的。</p>\n<p>从给定消息的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/hash\">hash</a>，<strong>签名过程</strong>首先使用实体的私有<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Key\">key</a>生成链接到签名实体的数字签名。</p>\n<p>收到消息后的<strong>验证过程</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><em>验证发件人</em> <em>-</em> 使用发件人的公钥来<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption\">解码</a>签名并恢复只能用发件人的私钥创建的哈希</li>\n  <li><em>检查消息完整性 -</em> 将哈希与接收到的文档中新计算的哈希进行比较（如果文档被篡改，两个哈希将不同）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果私钥被泄密或收件人被欺骗地给出错误的公钥，系统就会失败。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基础知识","title":"基础知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_signature\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Digital signature</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n  <li>See <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Digest\">digest</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Encryption\">encryption</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"技术参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Security/Information_Security_Basics\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">信息安全基础 ​​​​​​​</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"签名或数字签名是 协议，表明消息是真实的。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Signature (security)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Signature (sécurité)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Signature (署名 (セキュリティ) )","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/signature/security","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/signature/security/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Signature","title":"签名"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Signature/Security","title":"签名（安全）"}],"pageTitle":"签名（安全） - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}